Just Posting to Facebook Isn’t Enough

Facebook is both a helpful ally and a conniving foe.

Let me explain: 

When it comes to Facebook business pages, publishing a post does not guarantee all your followers will see it. Whereas platforms such as Youtube show your followers everything you post, Facebook directs your posts to people they deem most interested.

If you merely post to Facebook, your customers might not see all your posts.  Therefore, you need to promote your posts to ensure your customers see it. 

This isn’t a conspiracy; it’s the economics of a growing platform. While others are busy complaining about the problem, you have the opportunity to capitalize on a low-cost way to get in front of thousands of potential customers.

Do that, and Facebook will be your helpful ally.
